params.name: clusters
params.description: The color clusters to use, of shape (n_clusters, 3) when color quantizing. Can be overriden by clustersin preprocess.

params.name: do_resize
params.description: Whether to resize the images dimensions to (size[height], size[width]). Can be overridden bydo_resize in preprocess.

params.name: size
params.type: Dict[str, int] optional, defaults to {"height" -- 256, "width": 256}):Size of the image after resizing. Can be overridden by size in preprocess.

params.name: resample
params.description: Resampling filter to use if resizing the image. Can be overridden by resample in preprocess.

params.name: do_normalize
params.description: Whether to normalize the image pixel value to between [-1, 1]. Can be overridden by do_normalize inpreprocess.

params.name: do_color_quantize
params.description: Whether to color quantize the image. Can be overridden by do_color_quantize in preprocess.
